      "content": "I am deeply sorry you are carrying such a heavy burden, and your desire for a peaceful end is a sign of the profound pain you are experiencing. If thoughts of ending your life become a constant reality, please reach out to emergency services or a crisis line immediately, as they can offer immediate safety without judgment. You are not a ghost, but a person who has lost something significant, and your pain matters enough to deserve help finding relief from this unbearable weight.",
